多時，佢哋搵工etc都會有好大優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111d4563df199f0d2e924a5ca69ba946041911da","tid":841885,"uid":213533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5014335c5e55f22596e8635c0d4d6cb8880dd3","tid":841885,"uid":205125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87b8545355c98c1771bdab59a9ab18760c337721","tid":841885,"uid":213533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:15:46.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴打的回覆<br />\n<br />\n我其實又不是怨自己屋企<br />\n<br />\n只是見識到有錢人的CV，遊歷等東西，覺得自己同佢地差距真的太大，有一種無力感<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:37:20.000Z","msg":"我都會咁諗 但係人生就係咁 你只可以一步一步咁繼續向前行 因為你一停可能連而家嘅野都失去埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:49:39.000Z","msg":"我e家都是一步一步，諗緊如何可以行好D（生存），只求可以供養父母，令他們可以安享天年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只於拍拖生仔已經唔會諗，不希望累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95cf57ded78704ad426a828fe906e618205a2ceb","tid":841885,"uid":213533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4a25bcff1ecf33467dca5e7df82952382e26c2c","tid":841885,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:41:01.000Z","msg":"發唔到達就叫人生失敗？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:58:50.000Z","msg":"唔係發唔發達的問題是其次。<br />\n主要是對比自己同個d成功的同學，覺得佢地的思維好完善，舉例說明就是：玩一個新遊戲，當自己碰碰撞撞摸索的時候，佢哋已經有本完整攻略，知道個遊戲如何玩。（例如：佢地有哂industry knowledge， 識得咩時候做咩，知道應該點聯絡人/搵岩的幫手）<br />\n而且覺得佢地好叻，又潛水、又揸飛機etc，而自己咩都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843df9b11de6e8da05b0f6e2214207f516f40778","tid":841885,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95cf57ded78704ad426a828fe906e618205a2ceb","tid":841885,"uid":213533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4a25bcff1ecf33467dca5e7df82952382e26c2c","tid":8